GG_SOUTHERN_FACILITY

Made by Rokusho @ FPSBanana.com

Rokusho39@Hotmail.com

Another map from the DeagleCup series I made a while ago, it is a small fast paced and action packed map with lots of strategic options.  The glass in unbreakable but can be shot through easily.

This map has 20 spawn points, comes with HDR and has soundscapes fully implemented.  The nav file is also included in the archive file.  Full radar and overview included as standard.
